  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rapid Water Survey Project*</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our innovation would pilot-test a novel &#x201C;Rapid Water Survey&#x201D; that overcomes traditional difficulties associated with measuring water access in slums. It empowers slum dwellers to participate in the data collection process, and ultimately hold governments accountable. It will also assess the accuracy of new survey questions designed by the WHO/UNICEF Joint Monitoring Program (JMP) to assess water quantity and reliability in the post-2015 agenda. We will pilot this project in Mumbai, building on our team&#x2019;s long-standing research and grassroots efforts. This pilot will lay the groundwork for a larger inter-disciplinary, action-oriented project to address the water crisis in Mumbai&#x2019;s slums.</narrative>
  </description>
